        public String prettify​(String indent,

        This method is called from the implementation of the prettify(String, String) method of the CBORPairList class.

        Parameters:
        indent - The indent inherited from the upper CBOR item.
        indentUnit - Additional indent that should be added when nested CBOR items are stringified.
